01:41:13.407 --> 01:41:16.785
Same with the Jacobis' cat.
No collar, but he knew.

01:41:17.786 --> 01:41:20.956
He knew about the padlock.
He knew about the pane of glass.

01:41:21.081 --> 01:41:23.292
