in the rubble.

01:53:36.400 --> 01:53:39.236
- They're not Dolarhyde's.
- What are you talking about?

01:53:39.653 --> 01:53:42.406
<i>- His damn dentures were there.
- But not his bones.</i>

01:53:42.489 --> 01:53:43.740
