01:57:25.170 --> 01:57:26.964
<i>Where are you guys?</i>

01:57:28.966 --> 01:57:30.926
<i>I thought I heard
some kind of...</i>

01:57:32.928 --> 01:57:34.096
<i>Will?</i>

01:57:34.972 --> 01:57:36.640
Molly, get down!

01:57:50.654 --> 01:57:51.822
Will!

01:58:04.626 --> 01:58:06.170
Shoot...

01:58:07.838 --> 01:58:08.797
What?

01:58:08.881 --> 01:58:10.799
Shoot him. Shoot him.

01:58:28.400 --> 01:58:29.568
Mummy?

01:58:42.873 --> 01:58:45.751
<i>LECTER My dear Will:
You must be healed by now.</i>

01:58:46.460 --> 01:58:48.545
<i>On the outside, at least.</i>

01:58:48.670 --> 01:58:50.881
<i>I hope you're not too ugly.</i>

01:58:51.006 --> 01:58:53.634
<i>What a collection of scars
you have!</i>

01:58:53.759 --> 01:58:56.011
<i>Never forget
who gave you the best of them.</i>

01:58:56.094 --> 01:58:57.513
<i>And be grateful.</i>

01:58:57.596 --> 01:59:01.558
<i>Our scars have the power
to remind us the past was real.</i>

01:59:02.434 --> 01:59:04.895
<i>We live in a primitive time,
don't we, Will?</i>

01:59:04.978 --> 01:59:07.105
<i>Neither savage nor wise.</i>

01:59:07.189 --> 01:59:08.816
<i>Half measures
are the curse of it.</i>

01:59:09.107 --> 01:59:13.195
<i>A rational society would either
kill me or put me to some use.</i>

01:59:15.781 --> 01:59:18.867
<i>Do you dream much, Will?
I think of you often.</i>

01:59:20.035 --> 01:59:22.788
<i>Your old friend,
Hannibal Lecter.</i>

01:59:41.849 --> 01:59:44.059
<i>Hannibal?
There's someone here to see you.</i>

01:59:44.351 --> 01:59:47.688
<i>Wants to ask a few questions.
I said you'd probably refuse.</i>

01:59:49.148 --> 01:59:52.401
A young woman.
Says she's from the FBI.

01:59:52.484 --> 01:59:55.487
Though she's far too pretty,
if you ask me.

01:59:56.822 --> 01:59:58.991
I'll tell her you said no.

02:00:04.538 --> 02:00:06.248
What is her name?

